attributes.description: Visualization providing statistics about indicators ingested from the Threat Intelligence integration
attributes.title: [Logs Threat Data] Overview

params.markdown:
**Overview**

This dashboard is a health overview of the data provided by [threat intelligence integrations](/app/integrations/browse/threat_intel) with the Elastic Agent.

In order for this dashboard to display values, one or more threat intelligence integrations must be enabled from the Integrations page, or custom threat intelligence must be written to a logs-ti-* index or data stream in an ECS-compatible format.

The dashboard provides general statistics and shows the health of the ingestion of indicators. It shows the number of feeds enabled along with ingestion rates and provides a few filters for drilling down to specific feeds.
